Package: chatbotr
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Chatbot Application with Offcanvas Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Freeman", "Wang", , "freestatman@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application that provides an interactive chatbot interface 
    using an offcanvas (slide-out) panel. Integrates with shinychat and ellmer
    for AI-powered conversations. The package includes modules for building
    chatbot interfaces and a ready-to-run application.
